title: Bud Tucker in Double Trouble [ENG][OGG][for ScummVM]
description:
Bud Tucker in Double Trouble

An evil megalomaniac, A plot for world domination, A teenager with lame    
looking hair. Double trouble is the new cartoon adventure game from        
Merit studios. A professor is kidnapped and his duotronic replicator stolen, 
it is up to bud to save the world from the criminal mastermind.


Sounds, music and speeches were compressed with the newest oggenc and it's only working with ScummVM 0.13.0 and up.

Get it here - http://www.scummvm.org/downloads.php/


Hot keys:                                                                  
F1 - Swaps icons to text on Bud's action screen.                           
F2 - Switches character on-screen text ON and OFF.                         
F3 - Offers help in the initial screens only.
